[The case fatality rate suggested by this report is high. Assuming that
the diagnoses are correct, this outbreak serves to remind us of the danger
of pertussis in unvaccinated children. Sometimes emotional discussions of
the pros and cons of vaccination tend to forget the lessons of history. -
